# Repository Restructuring Complete ✅

## New Directory Structure

### Before:
```
environments/
  ├── dev/
  │   ├── distributions.tf     # CloudFront
  │   ├── lambda.tf            # Lambda
  │   ├── backend.tf           # Shared state
  │   └── ...
