## Benefits

### 1. **Complete Isolation** ✅
- CloudFront changes → Only CloudFront workflow runs
- Lambda changes → Only Lambda workflow runs
- No cross-contamination

### 2. **Independent Deployments** ✅
```
Change config/dev/distributions.yaml
  ↓
Only cloudfront-deployments workflow triggers
  ↓
Only CloudFront infrastructure deployed
  ↓
Lambda infrastructure untouched
```

```
Change config/dev/lambdas.yaml
  ↓
Only lambda-deployments workflow triggers
  ↓
Only Lambda infrastructure deployed
  ↓
CloudFront infrastructure untouched
```

### 3. **Separate State Management** ✅
- Each stack has its own state file
- No state conflicts
- Can destroy one without affecting the other
- Clearer blast radius

### 4. **Faster CI/CD** ✅
- Workflows only run when relevant files change
- No unnecessary validations
- Parallel execution possible

